{
  "stem": "7094.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not when we were in a group, but when we were on our own, I could-- this was a sort of wonderful support, in a way, that for one minute in a week, you know, or one five minutes, I could go back and to be myself.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was a great help at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I helped him in a way, because he was involved with a German woman.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was dangerous, because three of the Polish boys were hanged.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you didn't have-- you-- you were not supposed to mix the races, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And therefore it was-- the danger of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he had a girlfriend, so all the time with him I was talking about his girlfriend, trying to-- to encourage him that he should rather leave this German woman and be with his girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in a way, it got convenient-- it was convenient for me to encourage this relationship with his girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was a comfort, because for a little while I could be myself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But all the stages, I have never believed that I will survive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I always-- not one-- even-- which was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Somehow, this-- this-- this-- my grandmother saying, 'there's oil on top of the water,' I said, somehow, it must come.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Germans, who are so methodical, so exact, so bureaucratic, it must come out somehow, somewhere, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So all the time I have lived on the edge of life and death.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All the time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It-- it-- it needed-- I mean, work was, in a way, good, because I occupied myself with the work I did.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the tensions and the-- the-- the pressures and the fear-- this-- this-- the this is-- that-- that somehow it will come to an end.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
